{"lemma":"بادِرَةٌ","slug":"بادِرَةٌ","root":"ب.د.ر","root_slug":"ب-د-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ب-د-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n1975","n1986"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%AF%D9%90%D8%B1%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"sign, token, gesture sensu lato"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n1975","headword_ar":"بادرهُ","root":"bdr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mubaAdarapN","text_ar":"مُبَادَرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bidaArN","text_ar":"بِدَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Abtdrhu","text_ar":"ابتدرهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":";"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He hastened,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made haste,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strove to be first"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beforehand, in doing"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"attaining"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"obtaining"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K, TA, TK;) namely, a thing: (M:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gayoruhu A_ilayohi","text_ar":"غَيْرُهُ اـِلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"badara","text_ar":"بَدَرَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bAdrhu Alyh","text_ar":"بادرهُ اليه"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (M;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He hastened with another,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vied"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strove with him in hastening, to it"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to do"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"attain"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"obtain it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAjalahu","text_ar":"عَاجَلَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K, TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asoraEa A_ilayohi","text_ar":"اَسْرَعَ اـِلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bAdr","text_ar":"بادر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as well as ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"badara","text_ar":"بَدَرَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Abtdr","text_ar":"ابتدر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"] denotes mutual effort only when it is immediately trans.: when it is trans. by means of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ilaY","text_ar":"اـِلَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bi","text_ar":"بِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(the former in the TA written by mistake"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ElY","text_ar":"على"},{"kind":"text","text":"], there is nothing to show that it denotes this. (MF.) [But it is often immediately trans. without its denoting such effort.] One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bAdrhu","text_ar":"بادرهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He hastened to do it"},{"kind":"text","text":"[&c., as explained above]; meaning, a thing that he desired, or wished for: (TA:) [and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bAdrbihi","text_ar":"بادربِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the same;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he hastened with it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the former signifies also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he betook himself early to him"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bAdr A_ilayohi","text_ar":"بادر اـِلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he hastened to it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A;) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alyh","text_ar":"اليه"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"badara","text_ar":"بَدَرَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, Msb,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buduwrN","text_ar":"بُدُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, Msb:) or, accord. to Zj, agreeably with its derivation, [see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"badorN","text_ar":"بَدْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he employed the fulness of his power,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"force, to hasten"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^amorN","text_ar":"الاَمْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"badarahu","text_ar":"بَدَرَهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"badara","text_ar":"بَدَرَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ilayohi","text_ar":"اـِلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"badorN","text_ar":"بَدْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", TA, [or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buduwrN","text_ar":"بُدُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as above,])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"event, came to him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"happened to him, hastily, quickly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"speedily;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beforehand"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"before he expected it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eajila","text_ar":"عَجِلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sabaqa","text_ar":"سَبَقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aisotabaqa","text_ar":"اِسْتَبَقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) [and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"minohu qawolN","text_ar":"مِنْهُ قَوْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"badara","text_ar":"بَدَرَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiEolN","text_ar":"فِعْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a saying,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an action, proceeded from him hastily, without premeditation:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAdirapN","text_ar":"بَادِرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] It is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAdiruwA biAloA^aEomaAli haramFA","text_ar":"بَادِرُوا بِالْاَعْمَالِ هَرَمًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Strive ye to be before decrepitude with good works;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to perform them before decrepitude"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (El-Jámi' es- Sagheer.) And in another,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAdiruwA AlS~uboHa biAlowitori","text_ar":"بَادِرُوا الصُّبْحَ بِالْوِتْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Strive ye to be before daybreak with the prayers termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wtr","text_ar":"وتر"},{"kind":"text","text":"; i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to perform them before daybreak"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Idem.) And in another,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAdiruwA biSalAapi","text_ar":"بَادِرُوا بِصَلاَةِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Almagoribi qabola TuluwEi Aln~ajomi","text_ar":"المَغْرِبِ قَبْلَ طُلُوعِ النَّجْمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Hasten ye with,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to perform, the prayer of sunset before the rising of the star"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Idem.) You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN yubaAdiru fiY","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ يُبَادِرُ فِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^akoli maAli Alyatiymi","text_ar":"اَكْلِ مَالِ اليَتِيمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one hastens in consuming the property of the orphan"},{"kind":"text","text":"before the latter is of full age]. (A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAdara kibara Alyatiymi","text_ar":"بَادَرَ كِبَرَ اليَتِيمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He hastened to be before the orphan's attaining to full age in expending his property"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; said of a guardian;"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiy maAli Alyatiymi","text_ar":"فِي مَالِ اليَتِيمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^abodara","text_ar":"اَبْدَرَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) and thus,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bidaArFAA^ano","text_ar":"بِدَارًااَنْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yakobaruwA","text_ar":"يَكْبَرُوا"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the Kur [iv. 5], means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hastening to be before their attaining to full age"},{"kind":"text","text":"in expending their property. (Bd, * Jel.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bAdrhu AlgaAyapa","text_ar":"بادرهُ الغَايَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ilaY AlgaAyapi","text_ar":"اـِلَى الغَايَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He strove with him in hastening,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strove to get before him, to the goal"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlgaAyapa","text_ar":"الغَايَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Abtdr","text_ar":"ابتدر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ilaY AlgaAyapi","text_ar":"اـِلَى الغَايَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He strove in hastening,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strove to get first, to the goal"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Ham p. 46.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAdara baEoDuhumo baEoDFA A_ilaY A^amorK","text_ar":"بَادَرَ بَعْضُهُمْ بَعْضًا اـِلَى اَمْرٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^amorFA","text_ar":"اَمْرًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AbtdrwA","text_ar":"ابتدروا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tbAdrwhu","text_ar":"تبادروهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They vied,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strove, one with another, in hastening to a thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an affair, trying which of them would be first."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T.)"}],"source_refs":["M","K","TA","S","Mgh","Msb"]},{"entry_id":"n1986","headword_ar":"بَادِرَةٌ","root":"bdr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Hastiness of temper; passionateness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a hasty saying,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"action, that suddenly proceeds"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaboduru","text_ar":"يَبْدُرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaboduw","text_ar":"يَبْدُو"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from one in anger:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, A, * Mgh, * Msb, * K:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a slip; a mistake; an error;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"on an occasion of one's being angry:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a bad, an abominable,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a foul, word"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"saying:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a quick fit of anger:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, T:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bawaAdiru","text_ar":"بَوَادِرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axo$aY","text_ar":"اَخْشَى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealayoka baAdiratahu","text_ar":"عَلَيْكَ بَادِرَتَهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I fear for thee his hastiness of temper,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"passionateness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what may hastily proceed from him in his anger."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"minohu yawaAdiru gaDabK","text_ar":"مِنْهُ يَوَادِرُ غَضَبٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"badarato","text_ar":"بَدَرَتْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Slips, mistakes,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"errors, on an occasion of his being angry, hastily proceeded from him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAdirapu Al$~ar~i","text_ar":"بَادِرَةُ الشَّرِّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What hastily,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"suddenly, befalls one, of evil,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mischief."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An intuitive knowledge, notion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"idea;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a faculty of judging rightly at the first of an unexpected occurrence;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a faculty of extemporizing;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"badiyhahN","text_ar":"بَدِيهَهٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, K.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnu Hasanu AlbaAdirapi","text_ar":"فُلَانُ حَسَنُ البَادِرَةِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one has a good intuitive knowledge,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c. (TA.) ―         -b3-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"point"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a sword. (M, K.) ―         -b4-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extremity"},{"kind":"text","text":"of an arrow,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"next the head."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) ―         -b5-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"head"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a plant; (M;) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"first part"},{"kind":"text","text":"thereof"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from which the earth cleaves asunder."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K. *) ―         -b6-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"first that appears"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the [plant called]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hin~aA='","text_ar":"حِنَّا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M.) ―         -b7-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"leaves of the [herb called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Huw~aA='ap","text_ar":"حُوَّا=ءَة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b8-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"best, and freshest in growth, of the [plant called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waros","text_ar":"وَرْس"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M, K. *) ―         -b9-  Also, (M, K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bawaAdiru","text_ar":"بَوَادِرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A,) which is the pl., (K,) of a man &c., (S, M,) The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"portion of flesh,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K,) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"portions thereof,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"between the shoulder-joint and the neck,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"between the necks and the shoulderjoints:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A:) or the former, (K,) or its dual, (M,) of a man, the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"two portions of flesh that are above the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rugavaAwaAni","text_ar":"رُغَثَاوَانِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and below the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vanoduwap","text_ar":"ثَنْدُوَة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M, K:) or the dual, [relating to a camel, signifies] the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"two sides of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kirokirap","text_ar":"كِرْكِرَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"callous lump on the breast"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"two veins on either side thereof."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.) ―         -b10-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bawaAdiru Alxayoli","text_ar":"بَوَادِرُ الخَيْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"badarato","text_ar":"بَدَرَتْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The first,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fore parts,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^awaAy^il","text_ar":"اَوَايِل"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the horses appeared"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"suddenly came in view"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Msb.)"}],"source_refs":["S","IAar","T","M","K","A"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}